d/boe_icty_161104.pdf |archive-date=2011-06-07 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n* [[Mom\u010dilo Mandi\u0107]], Republika Srpska Justice minister,<ref>http://www.sense-agency.com/en/stream.php?sta=3&pid=5935&kat=3</ref> was born in Kalinovik.<ref>http://www.sudbih.gov.ba/?opcija=predmeti&id=31&jezik=e</ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[Municipalities of Republika Srpska]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Kalinovik}}\n* {{official website|http://kalinovik.info/}}\n\n{{Political divisions of Bosnia and Herzegovina}}\n\n[[Category:Populated places in Kalinovik]]\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Republika Srpska]]\n[[Category:Municipalities of Republika Srpska]]\n", "name_user": "EcLiPsE285", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kalinovik"}
