{"title_page": "Stanis\u0142aw Lubomirski (1722\u20131782)", "text_new": "{{For|other people of this name|Stanis\u0142aw Lubomirski (disambiguation)}}\n{{Unreferenced|date=December 2009}}\n{{Infobox noble|type\n| name              = Stanis\u0142aw Lubomirski\n| title             = \n| image             = Stanis\u0142aw Lubomirski.PNG\n| image_size        = 250\n| caption           = \n| alt               = \n| CoA               = [[Lubomirski coat of arms|Lubomirski]]\n| more              = no \n| reign             = \n| reign-type        = \n| predecessor       = \n| successor         = \n| suc-type          = \n| succession        = \n| spouse            = [[El\u017cbieta Czartoryska (1736\u20131816)|El\u017cbieta Czartoryska]]\n| issue             = [[El\u017cbieta Lubomirska]]<br>[[Julia Lubomirska (1764\u20131794)|Julia Lubomirska]]<br>[[Aleksandra Lubomirska]]<br>[[Konstancja Ma\u0142gorzata Lubomirska]]\n| issue-link        = \n| issue-pipe        = \n| full name         = \n| styles            = \n| titles            = \n| noble family      = [[Lubomirski]]\n| house-type        = \n| father            = [[J\u00f3zef Lubomirski]]\n| mother            = [[Teresa Mniszech]]\n| birth_date        = {{birth date|1722|12|25}}\n| birth_place       = [[\u0141a\u0144cut]]\n| christening_date  = \n| christening_place = \n| death_date        = {{death date and age|1782|8|12|1722|12|25}}\n| death_place       = \u0141a\u0144cut\n| burial_date       = \n| burial_place      = \n| occupation        = \n}}\n\nPrince '''Stanis\u0142aw Lubomirski''' (December 25, 1722 \u2013 August 12, 1782) was a [[Poland|Polish]] [[Szlachta|nobleman]]. He was awarded Knight of the [[Order of the White Eagle (Poland)|Order of the White Eagle]] on August 3, 1757 in [[Warsaw]], and later was also awarded the [[Order of Saint Stanislaus]].\n\nHe was the [[Grand Guardian of the Crown]] from 1752, onward, the [[Grand Marshal of the Crown]] starting in 1766, and the owner of [[\u0141a\u0144cut]], [[Wi\u015bnicz]] and [[Przeworsk]] estates.\n\nHe was married to Princess Izabela Czartoryska since June 9, 1753 and they had four children: [[El\u017cbieta Lubomirska]], [[Julia Lubomirska (1764\u20131794)|Julia Lubomirska]], [[Aleksandra Lubomirska]] and [[Konstancja Ma\u0142gorzata Lubomirska]]. His houses included [[Lubomirski Palace, Lviv|Lubomirski Palace]] in [[Lwow]]. He is also the namesake for [[Warsaw]]'s [[Lubomirski Ramparts]].\n\n{{Marshals GC}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Lubomirski, Stanislaw}}\n[[Category:Secular senators of the Polish\u2013Lithuanian Commonwealth]]\n[[Category:Members of the Sejm of the Polish\u2013Lithuanian Commonwealth]]\n[[Category:1722 births]]\n[[Category:1782 deaths]]\n[[Category:Lubomirski family|Stanislaw Lubomirski 1722]]\n\n\n{{Poland-noble-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{For|other people of this name|Stanis\u0142aw Lubomirski (disambiguation)}}\n{{Unreferenced|date=December 2009}}\n{{Infobox noble|type\n| name              = Stanis\u0142aw Lubomirski\n| title             = \n| image             = Stanis\u0142aw Lubomirski.PNG\n| image_size        = 250\n| caption           = \n| alt               = \n| CoA               = [[Lubomirski coat of arms|Lubomirski]]\n| more              = no \n| reign             = \n| reign-type        = \n| predecessor       = \n| successor         = \n| suc-type          = \n| succession        = \n| spouse            = [[El\u017cbieta Czartoryska (1736\u20131816)|El\u017cbieta Czartoryska]]\n| issue             = [[El\u017cbieta Lubomirska]]<br>[[Julia Lubomirska (1764\u20131794)|Julia Lubomirska]]<br>[[Aleksandra Lubomirska]]<br>[[Konstancja Ma\u0142gorzata Lubomirska]]\n| issue-link        = \n| issue-pipe        = \n| full name         = \n| styles            = \n| titles            = \n| noble family      = [[Lubomirski]]\n| house-type        = \n| father            = [[J\u00f3zef Lubomirski]]\n| mother            = [[Teresa Mniszech]]\n| birth_date        = {{birth date|1722|12|25}}\n| birth_place       = [[\u0141a\u0144cut]]\n| christening_date  = \n| christening_place = \n| death_date        = {{death date and age|1782|8|12|1722|12|25}}\n| death_place       = \u0141a\u0144cut\n| burial_date       = \n| burial_place      = \n| occupation        = \n}}\n\nPrince '''Stanis\u0142aw Lubomirski''' (December 25, 1722 \u2013 August 12, 1782) was a [[Poland|Polish]] [[Szlachta|nobleman]]. He was awarded Knight of the [[Order of the White Eagle (Poland)|Order of the White Eagle]] on August 3, 1757 in [[Warsaw]]. \n\nHe was the [[Grand Guardian of the Crown]] from 1752, onward, the [[Grand Marshal of the Crown]] starting in 1766, and the owner of [[\u0141a\u0144cut]], [[Wi\u015bnicz]] and [[Przeworsk]] estates.\n\nHe was married to Princess Izabela Czartoryska since June 9, 1753 and they had four children: [[El\u017cbieta Lubomirska]], [[Julia Lubomirska (1764\u20131794)|Julia Lubomirska]], [[Aleksandra Lubomirska]] and [[Konstancja Ma\u0142gorzata Lubomirska]]. His houses included [[Lubomirski Palace, Lviv|Lubomirski Palace]] in [[Lwow]]. He is also the namesake for [[Warsaw]]'s [[Lubomirski Ramparts]].\n\n{{Marshals GC}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Lubomirski, Stanislaw}}\n[[Category:Secular senators of the Polish\u2013Lithuanian Commonwealth]]\n[[Category:Members of the Sejm of the Polish\u2013Lithuanian Commonwealth]]\n[[Category:1722 births]]\n[[Category:1782 deaths]]\n[[Category:Lubomirski family|Stanislaw Lubomirski 1722]]\n\n\n{{Poland-noble-stub}}\n", "name_user": "NotADev", "label": "safe", "comment": "He was also awarded the Order of Saint Stanislaus.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stanis%C5%82aw_Lubomirski_(1722%E2%80%931782)"}
